<div class="container">
  <h1>Offline-First Stablecoin System for Emergency & Disaster Relief</h1>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>Problem Statement</h2>
    <p>
      During disasters, relief fund distribution suffers from delays, misuse,
      lack of transparency, and poor internet connectivity.
      Beneficiaries often do not receive aid on time.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>Proposed Solution</h2>
    <p>
      A blockchain-based stablecoin system that enables fast, transparent,
      and controlled fund distribution directly to verified beneficiaries,
      even in offline or low-network areas.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>Key Features</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Offline-first transactions</li>
      <li>Stablecoin-based relief funds</li>
      <li>Category-restricted spending</li>
      <li>Geo-restricted usage</li>
      <li>Public audit trail</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>System Architecture</h2>
    <p>High-level overview of how authorities, blockchain, and beneficiaries interact.</p>
    <!-- You can add your images here -->
    <!-- <img src="architecture.png"> -->
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>Impact</h2>
    <p>
      Ensures aid reaches the right person at the right time,
      improves trust for donors, and reduces fund leakage.
    </p>
  </div>

